{"tid":277251,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"intern vs summer school?入黎投個票","createTime":"2017-06-09T12:25:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-29T00:14:06.000Z","uid":116052,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"003e19a767e783b0b653973bdd5344eed4566ef9","tid":277251,"uid":116052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:25:19.000Z","msg":"小弟下年final year<br />\nintern同summer school 都未試過<br />\n一到final year就2樣都冇機會<br />\n而家得返最後既暑假，想問下大家意見<br />\n<br />\nintern 人工$3000/月<br />\nsummer school 韓國3week 預用$3000<br />\n<br />\n大家會揀邊個?<br />\n玩or返工經驗?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e28e36340bad4bd23eddc2de64848cb9448f1a","tid":277251,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ce757c0c505d6aa999a3cafe2fb33e254761883","tid":277251,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T12:51:07.000Z","msg":"city?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去韓國邊間？<br />\n上年一個summer 兩樣嘢都做晒 又係去韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e03f548207426138542f5bf402bc0fef87e1056","tid":277251,"uid":116052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T14:32:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>city?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去韓國邊間？<br />\n上年一個summer 兩樣嘢都做晒 又係去韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟唔係city <br />\n詳細唔講 識我既人要起我底好易自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去Kyungnam University"},{"pid":"98f588ba1fda85019f292e83270e46f57b4c65be","tid":277251,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>city?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去韓國邊間？<br />\n上年一個summer 兩樣嘢都做晒 又係去韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟唔係city <br />\n詳細唔講 識我既人要起我底好易自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去Kyungnam University</blockquote><br />\n因為我見intern又係得3000蚊人工 又係去韓國summer school 個情況一模一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去果間u係首爾 市中心就多嘢玩啲 但我自己就覺得都係幾悶 瘋狂行街 行博物館同食嘢<br />\n豪玩豪買豪食一個月用咗一萬到<br />\n你果間唔係首爾 可能會再悶啲  韓國仲要無乜嘢係啱男人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要睇下你本身鐘唔鐘意韓國文化 我本身無聽kpop同睇韓劇 所以就唔係幾鐘意韓國<br />\n同埋好憎食泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地真係食乜都會跟碟泡茶比你<br />\n但去summer school其實都幾易識到外國朋友 韓國嘅年青人都好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec1dee179903708439bc6b81f5b9088ba2ca828a","tid":277251,"uid":116052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:00:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>city?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去韓國邊間？<br />\n上年一個summer 兩樣嘢都做晒 又係去韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟唔係city <br />\n詳細唔講 識我既人要起我底好易自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去Kyungnam University</blockquote><br />\n因為我見intern又係得3000蚊人工 又係去韓國summer school 個情況一模一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去果間u係首爾 市中心就多嘢玩啲 但我自己就覺得都係幾悶 瘋狂行街 行博物館同食嘢<br />\n豪玩豪買豪食一個月用咗一萬到<br />\n你果間唔係首爾 可能會再悶啲  韓國仲要無乜嘢係啱男人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要睇下你本身鐘唔鐘意韓國文化 我本身無聽kpop同睇韓劇 所以就唔係幾鐘意韓國<br />\n同埋好憎食泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地真係食乜都會跟碟泡茶比你<br />\n但去summer school其實都幾易識到外國朋友 韓國嘅年青人都好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我未去過韓國 都對韓國幾有興趣<br />\n係咪真係岩女人去多d?就算釜山個邊都係咁? <br />\n有冇韓妹識下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0f7d84cd5a8bff3ea5ea66f40f7a9e915bb543f","tid":277251,"uid":109127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T16:31:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>city?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 去韓國邊間？<br />\n上年一個summer 兩樣嘢都做晒 又係去韓國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟唔係city <br />\n詳細唔講 識我既人要起我底好易自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n去Kyungnam University</blockquote><br />\n因為我見intern又係得3000蚊人工 又係去韓國summer school 個情況一模一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我去果間u係首爾 市中心就多嘢玩啲 但我自己就覺得都係幾悶 瘋狂行街 行博物館同食嘢<br />\n豪玩豪買豪食一個月用咗一萬到<br />\n你果間唔係首爾 可能會再悶啲  韓國仲要無乜嘢係啱男人買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要睇下你本身鐘唔鐘意韓國文化 我本身無聽kpop同睇韓劇 所以就唔係幾鐘意韓國<br />\n同埋好憎食泡菜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地真係食乜都會跟碟泡茶比你<br />\n但去summer school其實都幾易識到外國朋友 韓國嘅年青人都好nice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為我未去過韓國 都對韓國幾有興趣<br />\n係咪真係岩女人去多d?就算釜山個邊都係咁? <br />\n有冇韓妹識下? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n識咩人睇下你reg咩course<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我讀果間係summer school期間最多嘅係新加坡人 超過一半嘅學生都係佢地 反而韓國人唔多 我係咁岩reg咗啲奇怪course先識到韓國人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n間大學應該會搞好多活動for summer school嘅學生 參加下應該會識到人 不過無乜韓國學生參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我無去過釜山就唔知啦 但感覺會多風景睇過首爾 舒服過首爾 買嘢應該就應該可能就少嘢買過首爾<br />\n但大部分鋪頭賣嘅嘢都係女人嘢嚟 好多女裝衫同唔同牌子嘅化妝品<br />\n首爾比我嘅感覺唔係幾好 周圍都好多人 鋪頭來來去去都係果幾間 又無乜自然靚境睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實最重要係你要比個目標自己 究竟去summer school係為咗乜 為咗學識獨立？ 識外國朋友？ 了解韓國文化？定真係純玩？純玩架話我覺得去韓國就唔值了<br />\n有咗個目標就自自然然有個方向 咁先去得有意義啦 無意義嘅話留番係香港做intern好過啦"},{"pid":"1a6a3c48c7122363e4f87842a7f1f